<h1 id='platforms'>Platforms</h1><h2 id='get-all-platforms'>Get All Platforms</h2>
<blockquote>
<p>The above command returns JSON structured like this:</p>
</blockquote>

<pre class="highlight json tab-json"><code><span class="p">[</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
        </span><span class="s2">"id"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
        </span><span class="s2">"provider"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"jira"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
        </span><span class="s2">"name"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"concertwithme"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
        </span><span class="s2">"is_enabled"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">false</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
        </span><span class="s2">"has_access"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">true</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre>

<p>Returns all platforms</p>
<h3 id='http-request'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>GET /platforms</code></p>
<h3 id='expand-parameters'>Expand Parameters</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>platformUsers</td>
<td>Platform user model</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id='get-a-platform'>Get a platform</h2>
<blockquote>
<p>The above command returns JSON structured like this:</p>
</blockquote>

<pre class="highlight json tab-json"><code><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"id"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"provider"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"jira"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"name"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"concertwithme"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"is_enabled"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">false</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"has_access"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">true</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre>

<p>Returns a platform by ID</p>
<h3 id='http-request-2'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>GET /platforms/&lt;ID&gt;</code> </p>
<h3 id='expand-parameters-2'>Expand Parameters</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>platformUsers</td>
<td>Platform user model</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id='change-platform-status'>Change platform status</h2>
<blockquote>
<p>The above command returns JSON structured like this:</p>
</blockquote>

<pre class="highlight json tab-json"><code><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"id"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"provider"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"jira"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"name"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"concertwithme"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"is_enabled"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">false</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"has_access"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">true</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre>

<p>Enables or disables a platform</p>
<h3 id='http-request-3'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>PUT /platforms/&lt;ID&gt;/change-status</code></p>
<h3 id='available-parameters'>Available Parameters</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>status</td>
<td>bool true or false</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
